title: "Cramer's Stop Trading: Microsoft's got a real AI product"
text: "CNBC's Jim Cramer discusses why investors should keep an eye on shares of Microsoft."

title: "Funding for AI Chipmakers Plummets as Nvidia Ascends"
text: "Nvidia's gain has reportedly been other chip startups' loss. The firm has become the go-to company for computer chips used in artificial intelligence (AI) processes
source_name: which has shut off the funding tap for the company's potential competitors

title: "Apple Extends Chip Deal With Qualcomm"
text: "Apple Inc. is extending an agreement to get modem semiconductors from Qualcomm Inc. for three more years
source_name: a sign that its ambitious effort to design the chips in-house is taking longer than expected. Qualcomm shares surged on the news."
